content:
Complaint Management provides a streamlined process for service agents to capture and submit client complaints directly from a Person Account record. Case agents can also track and monitor submitted complaints.

You can enable CRM Analytics and create a CRM App for Complaint Management, giving your customer experience managers prebuilt dashboards to gain insights on complaints.

Service agents can quickly capture customer complaints with a guided intake form.

A self-service portal can be set up for customers to file complaints directly on the portal.

Required editions: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled.

Watch a video to learn about Complaint Management.

Complaint Intake OmniScript Components can be customized to suit business needs.

Enable Complaint Intake Process in a Self-Service Portal allows customers to launch the complaint intake process directly from a self-service portal.

CRM Analytics for Complaint Management gives customer experience managers quick insights on customer complaints.
title: Complaint Management in Financial Services Cloud
